.:: Zebra puzzle ::.
Color: red, green, ivory, yellow, blue
Food: eggplant, grapefruit, pear, broccoli, watermelon
Game: backgammon, go, billiard, whist, poker
Beverage: coffee, tea, milk, orange-juice, water
Pet: dog, fox, zebra, horse, snails

1. Food:eggplant == Color:red
2. Food:grapefruit == Pet:dog
3. Beverage:coffee == Color:green
4. Food:pear == Beverage:tea
5. Color:green is to the right of Color:ivory
6. Game:backgammon == Pet:snails
7. Game:go == Color:yellow
8. Beverage:milk is in the middle
9. Food:broccoli is on the far left
10. Game:billiard is on the left or right of Pet:fox
11. Game:go is to the left or right of Pet:horse
12. Game:whist == Beverage:orange-juice
13. Food:watermelon == Game:poker
14. Food:broccoli is to the left or right of Color:blue

.:: Answer ::.
